Flog.RayTracer.Insane

66430-sphere "Sphereflake" Demo

Warning: This is very CPU intensive. Your browser may appear to stop responding.

This extreme demo includes more than 30,000 times the number of objects, double the light count, and a canvas with 56% more pixels! Scattered about are few other enhancements where needed.

N-Tree is a Bounding Volume Hierarchy.

None is a the default "naive" ray tracer performing > 66k intersection tests per ray.
